It is not the action of the dance, the singing or the touch itself, but the personality of the artist, his character, that captivates with his art the public.
The search for an encounter with the essential, with the goblin that becomes visible in a way of feeling, of being and of being are and have been the constant of this work that is presented these days in the gallery El Fotómata.
